product.title: Balloon Squeaky Dog Toy
product.body-html:
The Balloon Squeaky Dog Toy is shaped like a balloon animal and comes in a pastel green shade. It can be used by dogs of all ages and breeds during playtime. Your pup will enjoy the bounce on this unusually shaped dog squeaker. It offers a loud high-pitched squeak when chewed. Made from a lightweight synthetic rubber (TPR) that has good tear strength and abrasion resistance. This toy is non-toxic and won’t wear down your dog’s teeth and is available in five unique shapes. 

  • Size: H14cm x W13.5cm
  • Before buying this toy, please ensure that it is suitable for your pet's preference, chewing habits, and size.

product.title: Blue Travel Water Bottle
product.body-html:
The perfect solution for keeping your dog hydrated on-the-go. Designed for your dog to drink fresh water from the attached bowl without wasting a drop. Simply squeeze the bottle with one hand to fill the bowl and release to drain the excess water back in. The leak-tight innovative bottle includes a carabiner for easy clipping to your backpack, bag, or leash — ideal for hikes, beach visits, road trips, and walks around the neighborhood.

Features: 
- Squeeze to hydrate & release to drain
- Perfect for walks, runs, hikes + travel
- Leak-tight shut off
- Includes a carabiner
- Food Safe & BPA-Free
- No water wasted 
- Dishwasher safe

Specs - Holds 15oz
-7.5" tall x 3" bottom diameter
- Weighs 3.6oz

product.title: Brighton Raincoat
product.body-html:
The new BRIGHTON rain coat is waterproof and soft. The stretchy sleeve cuffs and bottom protect your pup from splashes and the hood is made adjustable for an easy fit. It is also packable into a pouch that is attached to the liner of the coat!

There is a collar attachment opening on the neck and a harness attachment opening on the back.

The collar can either be bottom down or up for an extra sharp look and a front button closure keeps the zipper intact while featuring a loop for name tags.

This lightweight coat is the perfect urban outwear to keep your pup clean and dry from seasonal showers!

  • Machine wash cold in mesh laundry bag, low spin and line dry
  • Use toothpaste and brush to remove stains
  • 100% nylon

product.title: Cactus Toy
product.body-html: This snuffle Cactus toy allows you to hide treats in between the 4 slots and the bottle knitted pot is filled with squeakers! Each pup plays differently and we recommend you to keep a close watch particularly during the first time a new play object is introduced. No toy is completely indestructible, so please supervise the play to ensure safety if you know your pup is not gentle with toys.
